T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"聽住先，唔好放鬆"},{"pid":"d19c2fdb789fcdfe27cf1ffa0cd55c6e0c02a31e","tid":1256303,"uid":11719,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"建制為保選票可以去得幾盡？"},{"pid":"a2128ddc0414ae7a58a7d24481109b1e3073027e","tid":1256303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"_ _ _ _ ，其言也善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6b0184107f9e42c664217991c2a92ae40a188c","tid":1256303,"uid":158888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"臨近選舉一個二個講人話"},{"pid":"7ed846c2cff997e10bea25462ab132949d349da1","tid":1256303,"uid":266274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec897777f0239c5e2d150123dbeb4cc435adcc8","tid":1256303,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"聽住先，唔好放鬆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"ec1645db8357bee524bdd5ea787936c747fd1dd9","tid":1256303,"uid":266274,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"建制現在兩邊不是人，為左選票做雙面人"},{"pid":"8aef55d2b478dd769736d2d1250d8a18810b6925","tid":1256303,"uid":213171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"為選票姐 唔係講人話<br />\n建制DQ法案委員會直上大會都好有責任"},{"pid":"be692eb8a0c91f98e736651d9fe7b58490690340","tid":1256303,"uid":188050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"小分析,不喜勿屌<br />\n<br />\n其實建制派基本盤一直都在,就算有無發生反送中以立法會的選舉制度九龍西6個位有2個建制派在數字上完全是合理分配,只不過因為dq加泛民自己on9先會在補選將位輸出去。<br />\n<br />\n由這種分配就會知邊個最想民建聯仆街?絕對不是泛民,因為佢地知民建聯點仆都影響不到最終格局,形成一種尸位素餐的心理。相反梁美芬,謝偉俊這類真正受過高等教育的大狀律師,成日比民建聯班土共食住,如果佢地係西環契仔契女的話,民建聯就係西環親生仔,你係老母會親邊個?<br />\n<br />\n今次的事綜觀整個過程,經民聯,自由黨等在修例上一直拖延甚至學泛民提出修訂,成為在議會中除了泛民外拖拉政府的小力量,間接將唯命是從的民建聯推向風暴口,現時民建聯進退失據的局面從建制派內部競爭的角度絕對是鼠王芬和法律超人所樂見。"},{"pid":"240f1738e63fc20a1987460bcdab14e28f6898c7","tid":1256303,"uid":129235,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuSP1g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuSP1g3.jpg&h=513b2253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0526fa3ae15e596d04a0fcfda78fe62c5efbfc2c","tid":1256303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44d9dd4aeb2487f298b9f472e150f3059ceb591","tid":1256303,"uid":107405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"之前好撚威架 又聲大大 又睇唔起市民 睇住本土泛民被DQ直頭目中無人 氣勢無兩添<br />\n做乜依家要扮死狗呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"537779874e9df8ef22fbecfd3aaa5ad711744cf0","tid":1256303,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"呢啲割蓆撚要幫佢地cap晒割前割後嘅說話<br />\n再落區幫佢大肆宣傳表揚佢"},{"pid":"e9922aa6e230aad4e95ad89d00bbd6be36997d38","tid":1256303,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537779874e9df8ef22fbecfd3aaa5ad711744cf0","tid":1256303,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"呢啲割蓆撚要幫佢地cap晒割前割後嘅說話<br />\n再落區幫佢大肆宣傳表揚佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6a880636a66ecdf9621ac4e4438f1e73ca3ad5","tid":1256303,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"想參選特首?"},{"pid":"a8cfcdbbb0d1f8ee0838a544cbd61afb6751c6f4","tid":1256303,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9922aa6e230aad4e95ad89d00bbd6be36997d38","tid":1256303,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537779874e9df8ef22fbecfd3aaa5ad711744cf0","tid":1256303,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:20:4